AMETEK, Inc. Item 5. Other Events On January 28, 2003, AMETEK, Inc. issued a press release to announce its full-year and fourth quarter 2002 results. A copy of such press release is attached as Exhibit 99(a). The information contained in said press release is hereby incorporated by reference in this Form 8-K. Item 7. Financial Statements and Exhibits. (c) Exhibit 2
