Mr. Beck joined AMETEK in 2004 as Vice President and General Manager, Power Systems and Instruments Division. Prior to joining AMETEK, Mr. Beck was with Danaher Corporation, where he held a variety of sales and general management positions. His final position, prior to joining AMETEK, was President, Danaher Precision Systems Division.
