On January 29, 2009, AMETEK announced that its Board of Directors approved a $75 million increase to the authorized level for repurchases of its common stock. This increased authorization will be added to the $68.5 million that remained available from previous authorizations approved by the Board of Directors in 2008. A copy of such press release is attached hereto as Exhibit 99.1.
