Item 8.01 Other Events.
On January 3, 2012, AMETEK, Inc. issued a press release to announce it has acquired Technical Manufacturing Corporation. A copy of such press release is attached as Exhibit 99.1. The information contained in said press release is hereby incorporated by reference in this Form 8-K.
